title: Where will Tony Romo end up?
itunes:title: Where will Tony Romo end up?
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Chris Wesseling & Gregg Rosenthal – discuss all the latest news from around the NFL including Jets cornerback Darrelle Revis being arrested, and a few offseason roster moves from the Jaguars and the Dolphins. Then, the heroes break down the most likely landing spots for Cowboys quarterback Tony Romo, and debate over which team would be the best fit.
